title: Spinach and artichoke lasagne
ingredients: ['cooking oil spray', '9 lasagne sheets', '1 onion, chopped', '4 cloves garlic, chopped', '415ml vegetable stock', '1 tablespoon chopped fresh rosemary', '300g marinated artichoke hearts, chopped', '285g frozen chopped spinach, thawed, drained and squeezed dry', '800g tomato-based pasta sauce, such as Dolmio', '340g grated mozzarella cheese, divided', '115g herb feta, crumbled']
